text: Lari is a given name which may refer to: * Lari Ketner (1977–2014), American basketball player * Lari Lehtonen (born 1987), Finnish cross-country skier * Lari Pittman (born 1952), Colombian-American artist and professor * Lari White (1965–2018), American country music singer ==See also== * Larry, another given name
title: Lari (given name)
